            <lg xml:id="TK563">
<l>veruvanta ceytoḻukum veṅkōla ṉāyi </l>
<l> ṉoruvanta mollai keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The cruel-sceptred king, who acts so as to put his subjects in fear, will certainly and quickly come to ruin.</l>
            </lg>
